    {
      "id": "model-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 70,
      "y": 505,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 210,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Architecture: Microservices with message-oriented middleware\n\nCommunication: gRPC (synchronous RPC) between services\n\nCoordination: Bully algorithm for leader election\n\nFailure Model: Crash-stop failures (processes may crash but\n                not exhibit Byzantine behavior)\n\nConsistency: Vector clocks track causal ordering of events\n\nReplication: Order executors run with 3 replicas for HA\n\nFault Tolerance: System self-heals via automatic leader election\n\nScalability: Horizontal scaling via Docker replicas",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 204,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "locked": false
    },
